abilities.name: Devour
abilities.description: Consumes an enemy or neutral creep, acquiring any special abilities that it possessed.

abilities.name: Scorched Earth
abilities.description: Carpets the nearby earth in flames which damage enemies, while also granting him increased movement speed.

abilities.name: Infernal Blade
abilities.description: Doom swings his burning sword, igniting the enemy. Stuns for 0.6 seconds and applies a 4 second burn that deals 25 + 1.25/2.5/3.75/5% of the target's Max HP as damage per second.

abilities.name: Devoured Ability
abilities.description: This slot will be replaced with abilities acquired using Devour.

abilities.name: Devoured Ability
abilities.description: This slot will be replaced with abilities acquired using Devour.

abilities.name: Doom
abilities.description: Inflicts a curse that prevents an enemy Hero from casting spells or using items, while taking damage over time. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter. DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel
abilities.upgrade_description: Will suspend Doom's duration while the affected unit is within 900 range. Also causes it to remove positive buffs from the target when cast, and break most passive abilities while active.
